[The best buffer of protection between rabies in
wild animals and yourself is vaccination of
domestic animals, including cattle. Furthermore
vaccination of cattle is much cheaper than the
loss of a production animal. - Mod.TG]

For the interactive HealthMap/ProMED map of El
Tambo, Colombia, see <http://healthmap.org/r/03UL>. - Mod.MPP]
